# Development Workflow & Commands

## Getting Started
Check [package.json](mdc:package.json) for available scripts and dependencies.

## Common Development Commands
```bash
# Start development server
npx expo start -c

# Run on specific platforms
npx expo start --ios
npx expo start --android
npx expo start --web

# Build for production
eas build --platform ios
eas build --platform android

# Update app over-the-air
eas update

# Run TypeScript check
npx tsc --noEmit
```

## Configuration Files to Reference
- [app.json](mdc:app.json) - Expo app configuration and metadata
- [eas.json](mdc:eas.json) - Build and update configurations
- [metro.config.js](mdc:metro.config.js) - Metro bundler settings
- [babel.config.js](mdc:babel.config.js) - Babel transpilation setup

## Styling Development
- Reference [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) for NativeWind configuration
- Check [global.css](mdc:global.css) for global styles
- Use Tailwind CSS IntelliSense extension for better autocomplete

## File References for Common Tasks
- **Adding new routes**: Create files in [app/](mdc:app) directory
- **New components**: Add to [components/](mdc:components) or feature-specific `_components/`
- **API integration**: Add services and query factories to [services/](mdc:services) directory
- **TanStack Query setup**: Configure queries, mutations, and query factories in services
- **Global state**: Implement in [store/](mdc:store) directory for client-side state
- **Utilities**: Add to [utils/](mdc:utils) directory
